title: Ep. 26 - How Ludwig Instantly Lost $50,000
description: Rest in peace, Nick. On this episode, Nick stays in his covid dungeon on Day 8 of his quarantine and he is replaced by an inflatable dinosaur. The remaining three handsome and strong Yard members discuss the new beef surfaced between Slime and Ludwig's mom, Ludwig's encounter with a rude Boston prick, and Aimen hallucinating the entire second leg of his trip.
